channel.title: 317 coder looking for some kind of team
channel.description:
MSN: *
I'm mobile so you can reach me at any time I'll respond if I'm not busy.
Info: Ok so basically I'm a facilitator I will do anything that you give me an I'll give 110% effort all the time even if I don't know how to do w/e is I'll find out how to do it. I'm also an idealist I have some good Ideas for servers and economys so just message me let me know what you need an I'll try my best to do it I only do 317 server coding so anything other than 317 don't ask me I'm also not good with regardless clients.
About me: here's some info about me I'm 16 years old I'm in 10th grade at high school this year I'm taking computer development classes as well as web page designing I'm also a varsity wrestler. I have been playing RSPS for about 4-5 years and coding for about 1 year I have experience in staff positions as well as owner/co-owner of some servers with my friends. I like servers where the staff talks to there players an everyone knows each other an gets a long that makes the community grow an more fun for the players an I know some ways to make a server like that.
Well i guess that's a little about me so I don't want to bore you guys to death so if there's anything you want to know message me on MSN only way you will get a hold unless I come on here an you get me while I'm online ok well thanks for reading
